data.description: Welcome to the country but not far from town as it is conveniently located between Seatonville, Ladd and Spring Valley.  3 beds with 2 full baths and 1452 square feet.  Sit on the back deck and look out onto your 1 Acre flat yard, perfect for outdoor activities.  Comes with a Generac generator.  The main floor has a nice open floor plan with the kitchen, living room and dining room open to one another.  Nice big Master bedroom.  Laundry conveniently located on the second floor by the bedrooms.  Attached 2 car garage and a detached 1 car garage.  Come take a look!!
